# ==================================================
# SECURITY - NEVER COMMIT THESE
# ==================================================
**/.env
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.test
**/.env.production
**/secrets.properties
**/application-*.properties
**/application-*.yml
!**/application-example.properties
!**/application-example.yml
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.cer
**/*.crt
**/credentials.json
**/service-account*.json
**/google-credentials.json

# API Keys & Secrets (any file containing these patterns)
**/*apikey*
**/*api-key*
**/*secret*
**/*password*
**/*token*
**/*credential*

